@startuml Sequence_Recruiter_Matching
title Nhà Tuyển Dụng - Gợi Ý Ứng Viên

actor Recruiter as "👔 Recruiter"
participant FrontEnd as "Frontend\nApp"
participant MatchingService as "Matching\nService"
database Database as "Database"

== Xem Gợi Ý Ứng Viên ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Gợi ý ứng viên"
FrontEnd -> MatchingService: GET /api/matching/candidates?jobId={id}&page=0&size=20
MatchingService -> Database: Get job requirements
Database --> MatchingService: Job details
MatchingService -> Database: Query CVs with similar skills
Database --> MatchingService: Candidate profiles
MatchingService -> MatchingService: Calculate match scores
MatchingService --> FrontEnd: Ranked candidates
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị danh sách

== Xem Chi Tiết Ứng Viên ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click vào candidate
FrontEnd -> MatchingService: GET /api/matching/candidates/{candidateId}/details\n?jobId={jobId}
MatchingService -> Database: Get candidate profile & CV
Database --> MatchingService: Full data
MatchingService -> MatchingService: Calculate match specifics
MatchingService --> FrontEnd: Detailed profile
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Xem chi tiết\n(Match score, skills, CV)

== Xem Match Score ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: (on candidate detail page)
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Match score: 85%
:Xem phân tích match;
:Kỹ năng trùng khớp;
:Kỹ năng thiếu;

== Liên Hệ Ứng Viên ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Liên hệ"
FrontEnd -> FrontEnd: Show contact options
Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Chọn: email / phone
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: Hiển thị thông tin liên hệ
:Gửi email mời phỏng vấn;

== Lưu Ứng Viên ==

Recruiter -> FrontEnd: Click "Lưu"
FrontEnd -> MatchingService: POST /api/matching/candidates/{candidateId}/save
MatchingService -> Database: Create saved candidate
Database --> MatchingService: OK
MatchingService --> FrontEnd: Saved
FrontEnd --> Recruiter: ✅ Lưu ứng viên

@enduml
